<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>平等 - 标签 - 无名老人</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/tags/%E5%B9%B3%E7%AD%89/</link><description>无名老人的文章</description><generator>Hugo 0.160.1 &amp; FixIt v0.4.5</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 20:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/tags/%E5%B9%B3%E7%AD%89/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>慧眼看人生</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/wise-eye-on-life/</link><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 20:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/wise-eye-on-life/</guid><description>&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="慧眼看人生"&gt;&lt;span&gt;慧眼看人生&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e6%85%a7%e7%9c%bc%e7%9c%8b%e4%ba%ba%e7%94%9f" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：慧眼、人生、苦、真爱、覆藏、超度、念佛、平等、孝顺、大乘&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;三界火宅，生死苦海，就是佛说的“世间皆苦”。而有些人认为根本不苦，大体上分成两种心态：一种人不愿意面对，也不敢面对，所以常用打压、转移、麻痹或逃避的办法来自欺。比如：喝闷酒、打麻将等等方式方法。再一种就是走夜路高声歌唱的壮胆心态，明知有苦，但若承认了，那明天还怎么过？承认苦就等于承认无力，承认有弱点，不愿暴露自己的弱点，所以不能承认有苦。比如：人们说的“打肿脸充胖子”亦如此义。故，人们常说“人生如戏”。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>学会识别真假</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/xue-fo-zhong-shou-zai-xue-hui-shi-bie-zhen-jia/</link><pubDate>Thu, 08 May 2025 13:32:48 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/xue-fo-zhong-shou-zai-xue-hui-shi-bie-zhen-jia/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="学佛众首在学会识别真假"&gt;&lt;span&gt;学佛众首在学会识别真假&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%ad%a6%e4%bd%9b%e4%bc%97%e9%a6%96%e5%9c%a8%e5%ad%a6%e4%bc%9a%e8%af%86%e5%88%ab%e7%9c%9f%e5%81%87" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：学佛众首在学会识别真假、佛法、觉悟、修行、智慧、真理、见性、大乘、涅槃、平等&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　很多人学佛时最关心的是“学什么”，却较少意识到在末世修学中，更先要解决的问题往往是“怎么辨别真假”。若真假不分，正邪不辨，那么越热心越容易被带偏。本文正是从这一现实困境出发，提醒修学者把辨别真假放在首位，而不是把一切都混为“都算佛法”。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>清净一心</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/2017%E5%8F%A4%E5%8E%866%E6%9C%8819%E6%97%A5%E5%96%84%E6%99%BA%E5%B8%88%E5%BC%80%E7%A4%BA/</link><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2017 14:08:12 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/2017%E5%8F%A4%E5%8E%866%E6%9C%8819%E6%97%A5%E5%96%84%E6%99%BA%E5%B8%88%E5%BC%80%E7%A4%BA/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="2017古历6月19日善智师开示"&gt;&lt;span&gt;2017古历6月19日善智师开示&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#2017%e5%8f%a4%e5%8e%866%e6%9c%8819%e6%97%a5%e5%96%84%e6%99%ba%e5%b8%88%e5%bc%80%e7%a4%ba" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：觉悟、修行、智慧、自性、大乘、涅槃、平等、学佛、佛法、真理&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　很多人学佛时，一听到“观”“忏悔”“大乘”“普贤行”这些词，就容易把它们理解成外在形式，或者只停留在文字领会之上，以为多听、多记、多谈就是修行的进步。可若不先弄清什么是正观，什么是邪观，什么是向内照见，什么是仍在妄心里打转，那么表面上在学佛，实际却可能离正道越来越远。本文这篇开示，核心就在于引人回到“识本心、见本性、明因果、入正观”这一条真正的修学路径。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>见性之人？</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/seeing-nature-with-sections/</link><pubDate>Sun, 02 Apr 2017 22:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/seeing-nature-with-sections/</guid><description>&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="何为真正的见性之人"&gt;&lt;span&gt;何为真正的见性之人？&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e4%bd%95%e4%b8%ba%e7%9c%9f%e6%ad%a3%e7%9a%84%e8%a7%81%e6%80%a7%e4%b9%8b%e4%ba%ba" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：见性、功德、六祖大师、平等、念念无滞、自性、达摩、法华经、实相、佛性&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;见性成佛，是禅宗乃至整个大乘佛法的核心。然而何为真正的见性？它与福德、功德有何区别？见性之人日常心行又有何特征？本文依六祖大师对见性与功德的精要开示，结合《法华经》、达摩祖师语录，层层剖析真正见性之人的内在境界与外显德相。原文一字不易，仅于各段前加小标题，并首尾略作导引与总结，以助读者契入实相。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>何为真正的见性之人</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%BA%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%81%E6%80%A7%E4%B9%8B%E4%BA%BA/</link><pubDate>Tue, 13 May 2014 12:44:16 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%BA%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%81%E6%80%A7%E4%B9%8B%E4%BA%BA/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="何为真正的见性之人"&gt;&lt;span&gt;何为真正的见性之人&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e4%bd%95%e4%b8%ba%e7%9c%9f%e6%ad%a3%e7%9a%84%e8%a7%81%e6%80%a7%e4%b9%8b%e4%ba%ba" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：何为真正的见性之人、智慧、自性、见性、平等、佛法、觉悟、修行、真理、人民&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　很多人一听“见性”，要么把它神秘化，以为那是极少数人才有的玄妙体验；要么又把它简单化，觉得自己懂几句道理、会说几句空义，就已经算是“见性”。但真正的问题在于：若心行没有变，烦恼没有减，执着没有松，所谓见性到底凭什么成立？本文正是围绕这一误区，追问何为真正的见性之人。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>六和敬</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E5%85%AD%E5%92%8C%E6%95%AC/</link><pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2014 10:51:06 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E5%85%AD%E5%92%8C%E6%95%AC/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="六和敬"&gt;&lt;span&gt;六和敬&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%85%ad%e5%92%8c%e6%95%ac" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
